fullplot: In a sunken castle underneath the earth, five strangers wake. They have no food. No memory. No water. And no way out. They don't know it yet, but they're capable of something they never imagined. They must organize and band together for the sinister adventure that awaits them.
plot: Five strangers wake up in what appears to be a dungeon, and in order to escape, they need to solve a bunch of deadly puzzles.
title: Game of Assassins
